text:
Oh. My. Gosh. 

One of our San Diego county supervisors ⁦@jim_desmond⁩ dug into the data and found that only 6 of our 195 deaths are “true” #COVID19 deaths. 

The other unfortunate souls were already ailing or dying of something else.  https://t.co/XG0hiSNkcO
